data.description: Welcome to a cozy home situated in the Northern Meadows Subdivision, offering comfort and convenience all in one place. With 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, this single-story abode is perfect for easy living. Step into the separate dining room adorned with charming arches that seamlessly lead to the living room. A practical breakfast nook awaits you in the kitchen, and a front porch adds a welcoming touch.Sunlight pours into the great room, illuminating the Spanish tile flooring that graces the kitchen, great room, and bathrooms. Bedrooms are adorned with laminate flooring for added comfort.
